{
  "arquivo": "ca04_12",
  "total": 50,
  "dialogos": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Good morning, big bro!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Good morning, Uesugi-san.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Hey, mornin'.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Did you sleep well last night?\\nDo you still feel tired?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "I got a massage before going to bed.\\nIt felt SO good!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Really now? I'm glad.\\nYou're a big help, Yotsuba,\\nfor taking care of her.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Oh, it's nothing much.\\nStretching after exercise is basic for good health.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(...I was a little surprised last night,\\n but Yotsuba is the same as usual.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Are we going out for breakfast today?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Yes, there are many shops on Kokusai dori%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Good morning, Fu-kun!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "WOAH?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Huh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Sorry to keep you waiting.\\nIt took me longer than expected to get ready.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I wasn't really waiting,\\nbut what's going on? That was kind of dangerous.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "You don't have to be embarrassed.\\nWe're close, aren't we?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I don't remember being THIS close.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Hmm? \\nDon't tell me you forgot about me, did you?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "U-um, Nino, good morning.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Oh, good morning, Yotsuba.\\nGood morning, Raiha-chan.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Gooood mooorning!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Hey, Nino! Isn't Miku with you?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Here I am.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "UHYAAA?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "When did you get behind me?\\nYou really surprised me!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "If you don't notice someone sneaking up from behind,\\nyou have too many openings.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "If this were the Sengoku era,\\nthe Yotsuba clan would be elimitated immediately.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Huh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Futaro, good morning.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Hey, morning, Miku.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Yesterday was so fun.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Yeah, for sure.\\nI'm glad you had fun too, Miku%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "But I don't have much stamina, and...\\nI bet you don't either, Futaro.\\nIf we get tired, let's take a break together, okay?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "H-hey, you two!\\nDon't get so close to me!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Good morning.\\nSorry to keep you waiting.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Ah, Itsuki! Morning.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Come on, Ichika.\\nWe've arrived at the lobby,\\nso please get yourself together.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Nnnnh...morninggg...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Ichika, are you awake?\\nOr, perhaps asleep?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Half-and-half, I guess.\\nThinking about how I don't have to work or study,\\nI kind of let my guard down...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "But, I'll be okay.\\nOnce I have breakfast,\\nI'll wake up...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Yeah, you're right.\\nWell, now that we're all here%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Hey, Fu-kun.\\nI'm hungry.\\nLet's go already.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "What do you want to eat, Futaro?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I said, get away from me.\\nIt's hard to walk.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 46,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Yotsuba?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 47,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Ah, yeah! Let's go!\\nTime to depart!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 48,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Alrighty.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 49,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "...Nino and Miku are serious, huh.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    }
  ]
}